rc=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界今晚集中火力 tag #sanukling # Chinazi #xinjiang #policestate #warcrime￼ <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家人權法唔系100%通過￼<br />\n可以加辣亦可以減辣<br />\n之前就受害者模式<br />\n依家就勝利者模式唱國歌<br />\n你估依家美國會唔會幫你加辣￼￼￼<br />\n未通過之前好心大家扮下野啦 ￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續唱美國國歌 揮美國國旗<br />\n同埋做好文宣 咩都好形造到我地有幾慘得幾慘￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7eaa98a531d59daf66e94892ae6bbe774de2dd","tid":1562871,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"shitty仔係時候出動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d574f8b0956e03957dbd69017fa236154bf9419c","tid":1562871,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0b36c50e424537b44b71277e4a85ddcf4820ef60","tid":1562871,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"2d460e24dc6018e209ff933df58aaf5ca5b30511","tid":1562871,"uid":77580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d7eaa98a531d59daf66e94892ae6bbe774de2dd","tid":1562871,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"shitty仔係時候出動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"屌去咗ifc"},{"pid":"c6cfb6d4c7fc57e7f048fe4afdbaa153d587965b","tid":1562871,"uid":220977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d7eaa98a531d59daf66e94892ae6bbe774de2dd","tid":1562871,"uid":214192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"shitty仔係時候出動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:36:29.000Z","msg":"仲有浸中"},{"pid":"bafd5e32ace8dbb880a31d0ea8604015b68a8fc7","tid":1562871,"uid":28480,